msg: JDO-591 add methods to get new metadata and to register the metadata with the enhancement process - equivalent to what we have on the PMF for the persistence process. Note that I've not added a getMetadata() method to view metadata of known classes, since the enhancement process will typically only load these when we need to enhance, whereas the persistence process loads when encountered for the first time
